snippet.title: My new massive multiplayer Web game: Master of the Grid
snippet.description:
Help me out, submit trivia challenges: http://db.masterofthegrid.net/
Play: http://masterofthegrid.net/

Master of the Grid is a multiplayer trivia game inspired by TV game shows but hosted by livestreamers on the Web. Up to 80 people at once try to answer questions for fun & prizes. Each player gets a cute animated, customizable 3D avatar. It's still a work in progress but it's coming soon!

Music is called Warped by tricksntraps (license CC0 - http://opengameart.org/content/free-music-pack)
